nodes.bodyText:
What is the purpose of e.getToVertex().getIncoming().contains(e) ? I think we should add a "business method" to edge witch make this easier to understand, and call that in the filter(...) method above:
boolean Edge.isConnectedToGraph() {
    return getToVertex().getIncoming().contains(this);
}

It might not be needed, if so we can delete it.

